{"tid":2496041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報英國將公布針對外國間諜新法案","createTime":"2021-04-19T14:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T14:39:19.000Z","uid":229777,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d8683457db38c2ad751bce5c9bebca44d59167c1","tid":2496041,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"英國傳媒報道，英國將會公布針對外國間諜的新法案以保護英國，免受有敵意的國家，如中國及俄羅斯的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n下月11日是英國國會開幕大典，首相約翰遜將會透過女王伊利沙伯二世的致辭公布新法案。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》報道，新法案會要求所有在英國，為外國政府工作的人必須進行登記，違者將被刑事檢控及驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n《每日郵報》報道，有情報組織曾警告，根據現行法例，除非外國間諜被揭發取得官方機密，否則不會受法律約束，相信新法案是想效法美國的《外國代理人登記法》，建立一個適用於任何代表外國政府人士的登記制度。<br />\n<br />\n據報，英國亦計劃更新《官方保密法》，將檢控對象擴大至任何企圖損害英國利益的海外人士以及外國黑客等，當局同時考慮提高相關罪行的最高刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=431682\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431682&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuMsFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=97e34d41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431682&h=f3de9c4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=431682</a>"},{"pid":"3b87bbb94e74ef3bfc61be2e7d98627c58a8b0a1","tid":2496041,"uid":144626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"好簡單，將大學堆cssa列作恐怖組織<br />\n不過英揆有冇咁夠薑？"},{"pid":"c8d23bef7571020e76ba448a68cfc2214f3df2af","tid":2496041,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"台灣有未"},{"pid":"d0b8052d8c4648b21b13ddba3edc2467a7ceff5f","tid":2496041,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\